8019 // clear edit profiles, models noises
8020 void US_ExperGuiUpload::clearData_protDev()
8021 {
8022 
8023  //Get proper filename
8024  QMap< QString, QString > protocol_details = mainw->protocol_details_passed;
8025  QString FileName = protocol_details[ "filename" ];
8026  QStringList fileNameList;
8027  fileNameList. clear();
8028  if ( FileName.contains(",") && FileName.contains("IP") && FileName.contains("RI") )
8029  fileNameList = FileName.split(",");
8030  else
8031  fileNameList << FileName;
8032 
8033  //show progress dialog
8034  int progress_total = fileNameList.size()*6 + 1;
8035  QProgressDialog* progress_msg = new QProgressDialog ("Cleaning Data for Current Run...", QString(), 0, progress_total, this);
8036  progress_msg->setWindowFlags(Qt::Tool | Qt::WindowTitleHint | Qt::CustomizeWindowHint);
8037  progress_msg->setModal( true );
8038  progress_msg->setWindowTitle(tr("Cleaning Data..."));
8039  progress_msg->setAutoClose( false );
8040  progress_msg->setValue( 0 );
8041  progress_msg->show();
8042  qApp->processEvents();
8043 
8044  progress_msg->setValue( 1 );
8045  qApp->processEvents();
8046 
8047  // Check DB connection
8048  US_Passwd pw;
8049  QString masterpw = pw.getPasswd();
8050  US_DB2* db = new US_DB2( masterpw );
8051 
8052  if ( db->lastErrno() != US_DB2::OK )
8053  {
8054  QMessageBox::warning( this, tr( "Connection Problem: Failed Run Cleanup" ),
8055  tr( "Read protocol: Could not connect to database \n" ) + db->lastError() );
8056  return;
8057  }
8058 
8059  int status;
8060  QStringList qry;
8061 
8062  int progress = progress_msg->value();
8063 
8064  /*** Iterate over fileNameList *********************************************/
8065  for ( int i=0; i<fileNameList.size(); ++i )
8066  {
8067  qry.clear();
8068  //get experimentID from 'experiment' table:
8069  qry << "get_experiment_info_by_runID"
8070  << fileNameList[ i ]
8071  << protocol_details[ "invID_passed" ];
8072 
8073  qDebug() << "clearData_protDev(), qry -- " << qry;
8074 
8075  db->query( qry );
8076  db->next();
8077  QString expID = db->value( 1 ).toString();
8078 
8079  progress_msg->setValue( ++progress);
8080  qApp->processEvents();
8081 
8082  // Let's make sure it's not a calibration experiment in use
8083  qry. clear();
8084  qry << "count_calibration_experiments" << expID;
8085  int count = db->functionQuery( qry );
8086  qDebug() << "Cleaning Failed Run: calexp count" << count;
8087 
8088  progress_msg->setValue( ++progress);
8089  qApp->processEvents();
8090 
8091  if ( count < 0 )
8092  {
8093  qDebug() << "count_calibration_experiments( "
8094  << expID
8095  << " ) returned a negative count";
8096  progress_msg->close();
8097  return;
8098  }
8099 
8100  else if ( count > 0 )
8101  {
8102  QMessageBox::information( this,
8103  tr( "Error" ),
8104  tr( "Cannot delete an experiment that is associated "
8105  "with a rotor calibration\n" ) );
8106 
8107  progress_msg->close();
8108  return;
8109  }
8110 
8111  int status;
8112  // Delete links between experiment and solutions
8113  qry. clear();
8114  qry << "delete_experiment_solutions"
8115  << expID;
8116  status = db -> statusQuery( qry );
8117  qDebug() << "Cleaning Failed Run: del sols status" << status;
8118 
8119  progress_msg->setValue( ++progress);
8120  qApp->processEvents();
8121 
8122  // Same with cell table
8123  qry. clear();
8124  qry << "delete_cell_experiments"
8125  << expID;
8126  status = db -> statusQuery( qry );
8127  qDebug() << "Cleaning Failed Run: del cells status" << status;
8128 
8129  progress_msg->setValue( ++progress);
8130  qApp->processEvents();
8131 
8132 
8133  // Let's delete any pcsa_modelrecs records to avoid
8134  // constraints problems
8135  qry. clear();
8136  qry << "delete_run_pcsa_recs"
8137  << fileNameList[ i ];
8138  status = db -> statusQuery( qry );
8139  qDebug() << "Cleaning Data (del pcsa_recs) for Run PRotDev(): del_exp stat" << status;
8140  //deleteRunPcsaMrecs( db, protocol_details[ "invID_passed" ], protocol_details[ "filename" ] );
8141 
8142  progress_msg->setValue( ++progress);
8143  qApp->processEvents();
8144 
8145  // // Now delete the experiment and all existing rawData,
8146  // qry. clear();
8147  // qry << "delete_experiment"
8148  // << expID;
8149  // status = db -> statusQuery( qry );
8150  // qDebug() << "Cleaning Failed Run: del_exp stat" << status;
8151 
8152  // if ( status != US_DB2::OK )
8153  // {
8154  // QMessageBox::information( this,
8155  // tr( "Error / Warning" ),
8156  // db -> lastError() + tr( " (error=%1, expID=%2)" )
8157  // .arg( status ).arg( expID ) );
8158  // }
8159 
8160  // Now delete editedData, models, noises, reports,
8161  qry. clear();
8162  qry << "clear_data_for_experiment"
8163  << expID;
8164  status = db -> statusQuery( qry );
8165  qDebug() << "Cleaning Data (del data) for Run PRotDev(): del_exp stat" << status;
8166 
8167  progress_msg->setValue( ++progress);
8168  qApp->processEvents();
8169 
8170  if ( status != US_DB2::OK )
8171  {
8172  QMessageBox::information( this,
8173  tr( "Error / Warning" ),
8174  db -> lastError() + tr( " (error=%1, expID=%2)" )
8175  .arg( status ).arg( expID ) );
8176  }
8177  }
8178 
8179  progress_msg->setValue( progress_msg->maximum() );
8180  qApp->processEvents();
8181  progress_msg->close();
8183 }

8185 // Slot to submit GMP run with Disk Data
8186 void US_ExperGuiUpload::submitExperiment_dataDisk()
8187 {
8188  /* IMPORTANT!
8189  Add filepath to the autoflow record:
8190  Add stage 'EDITING'
8191  */
8192  QMap< QString, QString > protocol_details;
8193 
8194  //dataPath
8195  protocol_details[ "dataPath" ] = rpRotor->importDataDisk;
8196  //stage/status
8197  protocol_details[ "status" ] = "EDITING"; // <--- ADD explicitly!
8198  //optimaName
8199  protocol_details[ "OptimaName" ] = "dataDisk"; // <--- OR NULL???
8200  //protocol_details[ "OptimaName" ] = rpRotor->instrname; // NULL
8201 
8202  QString dataSourceType = ( !rpRotor->importData_absorbance_t ) ? "dataDiskAUC" : "dataDiskAUC:Absorbance";
8203  protocol_details[ "dataSource" ] = dataSourceType; //<-- for now
8204 
8205  protocol_details[ "protocolName" ] = currProto->protoname;
8206  QString runname = mainw->currProto.runname;
8207  protocol_details[ "experimentName" ] = runname;
8208  protocol_details[ "label" ] = currProto->exp_label;
8209  //GMP type
8210  QString gmpRun_str = (mainw->usmode)? "NO" : "YES";
8211  protocol_details[ "gmpRun" ] = gmpRun_str;
8212  protocol_details[ "aprofileguid" ] = currProto->protoGUID;
8213 
8214  //compute duration: Get # satges, cells
8215  int nstages = sibIValue( "speeds", "nspeeds" );
8216  int tem_delay_sec = int((mainw->currProto.temeq_delay)*60); // delay in sec (longevity) of the dummy equlibration stage
8217  int nstages_size;
8218  nstages_size = tem_delay_sec ? nstages + 1 : nstages; // Total # stages
8219  //Total duration
8220  bool is_dummy_dur = false;
8221  int curr_stage_dur;
8222  int Total_duration = tem_delay_sec;
8223  for (int i=0; i<nstages_size; i++)
8224  {
8225  if (i==0 && tem_delay_sec)
8226  {
8227  is_dummy_dur = true;
8228  continue; // skip dummy stage for AbsScanParams
8229  }
8230 
8231  if (is_dummy_dur)
8232  curr_stage_dur = i - 1;
8233  else
8234  curr_stage_dur = i;
8235 
8236  qDebug() << "index i: " << i << ", curr_stage_DUR: " << curr_stage_dur;
8237 
8238  Total_duration += rpSpeed->ssteps[ curr_stage_dur ].duration;
8239  Total_duration += rpSpeed->ssteps[ curr_stage_dur ].delay_stage;
8240  Total_duration += rpSpeed->ssteps[ curr_stage_dur ].delay;
8241  //ALEXEY: do we need also delays to first scans for abs/interference into total duration?
8242  }
8243 
8244  protocol_details[ "duration" ] = QString::number(Total_duration);
8245 
8246  protocol_details[ "invID_passed" ] = currProto->investigator.split(":")[0];
8247  protocol_details[ "correctRadii" ] = QString("YES"); //<--- will it be "NO" ? (no Optima...)
8248  protocol_details[ "expAborted" ] = QString("NO");
8249  protocol_details[ "operatorID" ] = QString::number( rpRotor->operID );
8250  //define exp.Type
8251  QString exp_t = ( mainw->us_abde_mode ) ? "ABDE" : "VELOCITY";
8252  protocol_details[ "expType" ] = exp_t;
8253 
8254  //protocol_details[ "experimentId" ] = QString::number(ExpDefId); // NULL
8255 
8256  //Now, ranges, cells, triples
8257  int nwavl_tot = 0;
8258  for ( int kk = 0; kk < rpRange->nranges; kk++ )
8259  nwavl_tot += rpRange->chrngs[ kk ].wvlens.count();
8260 
8261  //Opt system check, what cells will be uvvis and/or interference
8262  QStringList oprof = sibLValue( "optical", "profiles" );
8263  QString uvvis = tr( "UV/visible" );
8264  QString rayleigh = tr( "Rayleigh Interference" );
8265 
8266  //get # cells with interference channels
8267  int ncells_interference = 0;
8268  int nchannels_uvvis = 0;
8269  QStringList active_channels;
8270  for ( int kk = 0; kk < oprof.count(); kk++ )
8271  {
8272  if ( oprof[ kk ].contains( rayleigh ) )
8273  {
8274  if ( oprof[ kk ].section( ":", 0, 0 ).contains("sample") )
8275  {
8276  qDebug() << "ITF channel name: " << oprof[ kk ].section( ":", 0, 0 ).split(",")[0];
8277  active_channels << oprof[ kk ].section( ":", 0, 0 ).split(",")[0];
8278  }
8279 
8280  ++ncells_interference;
8281  }
8282 
8283  if ( oprof[ kk ].contains( uvvis ) )
8284  ++nchannels_uvvis;
8285  }
8286 
8287  //CELLS & TRIPLES: when interference ? (divide by 2!!! )
8288  if ( ncells_interference !=0 && nwavl_tot == 0 ) //Interference ONLY
8289  {
8290  protocol_details[ "CellChNumber" ] = QString::number( int(ncells_interference/2 ));
8291  qDebug() << "ITF: CellChNumber: " << protocol_details[ "CellChNumber" ];
8292  protocol_details[ "TripleNumber" ] = QString::number(1 * int(ncells_interference/2 ));
8293  qDebug() << "ITF: TripleNumber: " << protocol_details[ "TripleNumber" ];
8294  }
8295  else if ( ncells_interference == 0 && nwavl_tot != 0 ) //Absorbance ONLY
8296  {
8297  protocol_details[ "CellChNumber" ] = QString::number( nchannels_uvvis );
8298  qDebug() << "UV: CellChNumber: " << protocol_details[ "CellChNumber" ];
8299  protocol_details[ "TripleNumber" ] = QString::number(nwavl_tot);
8300  qDebug() << "UV: TripleNumber: " << protocol_details[ "TripleNumber" ];
8301  }
8302  else if ( ncells_interference !=0 && nwavl_tot !=0 ) // BOTH
8303  {
8304  QString cellnumber = QString("IP:") + QString::number( int(ncells_interference/2 ) ) +
8305  QString(",RI:") + QString::number( nchannels_uvvis );
8306 
8307  protocol_details[ "CellChNumber" ] = cellnumber;
8308 
8309  qDebug() << "UV & ITF: cellnumber: " << cellnumber;
8310  qDebug() << "UV & ITF: CellChNumber: " << protocol_details[ "CellChNumber" ];
8311 
8312  QString triplenumber = QString("IP:") + QString::number(1 * int(ncells_interference/2 )) +
8313  QString(",RI:") + QString::number(nwavl_tot);
8314 
8315  protocol_details[ "TripleNumber" ] = triplenumber;
8316 
8317  qDebug() << "UV & ITF: triplenumber: " << triplenumber;
8318  qDebug() << "UV & ITF: TripleNumber: " << protocol_details[ "TripleNumber" ];
8319  }
8320 
8321  //create parent autoflow record:
8322  add_autoflow_record_dataDisk( protocol_details );
8323 
8324  //emit proper signal -> switch to 3. IMPORT
8325  emit expdef_submitted_dataDisk( protocol_details );
8326 }

8329 // Slot to submit for EDIT & ANALYSIS when US_ProtDev
8330 void US_ExperGuiUpload::submitExperiment_protDev()
8331 {
8332  QMap< QString, QString > protocol_details = mainw->protocol_details_passed;
8333 
8334  qDebug() << "PROT DETAILS COMPARISON: -- ";
8335  qDebug() << "Old, New protocolName: " << protocol_details[ "protocolName" ] << ", " << currProto->protoname;
8336  qDebug() << "Old, New experimentName: " << protocol_details[ "experimentName" ] << ", " << currProto->runname;
8337  qDebug() << "Old, New label: " << protocol_details[ "label" ] << ", " << currProto->exp_label;
8338  qDebug() << "Old, New aprofileguid: " << protocol_details[ "aprofileguid" ] << ", " << currProto->protoGUID;
8339 
8340  protocol_details[ "protocolName" ] = currProto->protoname;
8341  protocol_details[ "experimentName" ] = currProto->runname;
8342  protocol_details[ "label" ] = currProto->exp_label;
8343  //protocol_details[ "gmpRun" ] = QString("NO"); //ALEXEY: state explicitly
8344  protocol_details[ "gmpRun" ] = QString("YES"); //ALEXEY: state explicitly
8345  protocol_details[ "aprofileguid" ] = currProto->protoGUID;
8346  protocol_details[ "devRecord" ] = QString("YES"); //ALEXEY: state explicitly
8347 
8348  qDebug() << "PROTCOL DETAILS at submission: -- "
8349  << protocol_details[ "protocolName" ]
8350  << protocol_details[ "CellChNumber" ]
8351  << protocol_details[ "TripleNumber" ]
8352  << protocol_details[ "duration" ]
8353  << protocol_details[ "experimentName" ]
8354  << protocol_details[ "experimentId" ]
8355  << protocol_details[ "runID" ]
8356  << protocol_details[ "status" ]
8357  << protocol_details[ "dataPath" ]
8358  << protocol_details[ "OptimaName" ]
8359  << protocol_details[ "runStarted" ]
8360  << protocol_details[ "invID_passed" ]
8361  << protocol_details[ "correctRadii" ]

9463  }
9464 
9465  //Finish, emit, switch to 2. LIVE_UPDATE
9466  emit expdef_submitted( protocol_details );
9467 }

10036  createGMPRun_Json += "\"lname\":\"" + u_lname + "\",";
10037  createGMPRun_Json += "\"email\":\"" + u_email + "\",";
10038  createGMPRun_Json += "\"level\":\"" + QString::number( u_level ) + "\"";
10039  createGMPRun_Json += "}],";
10040 
10041  createGMPRun_Json += "\"Comment\": \"" + gmp_submitter_map[ "Comment:" ] + "\"";
10042 
10043  createGMPRun_Json += "}";
10044 
10045  qry. clear();
10046  qry << "new_autoflowStatusGMPCreate_record"
10047  << protocol_details[ "autoflowID" ]
10048  << createGMPRun_Json;
10049 
10050  qDebug() << "new_autoflowStatusGMPCreate_record qry -- " << qry;
10051 
10052  int autoflowStatusID = db->functionQuery( qry );
10053 
10054  if ( !autoflowStatusID )
10055  {
10056  QMessageBox::warning( this, tr( "AutoflowStatus Record Problem" ),
10057  tr( "autoflowStatus (GMP run CREATE): There was a problem with creating a record in autoflowStatus table \n" ) + db->lastError() );
10058 
10059  return;
10060  }
10061  qDebug() << "in record_GMPCreation_status: createGMPRun_Json -- " << createGMPRun_Json;
10062 
10063  protocol_details[ "statusID" ] = QString::number( autoflowStatusID );
10064 
10065  /************** finally, update autoflow record with StatusID: ****************/
10066  qry. clear();
10067  qry << "update_autoflow_with_statusID"
10068  << protocol_details[ "autoflowID" ]
10069  << QString::number( autoflowStatusID );
10070 
10071  qDebug() << "update_autoflow_with_statusID qry -- " << qry;
10072  db->query( qry );
10073 
10074  /************** IF ABDE - add record to the new 'autoflowAnalysisABDE' table ***/
10077  /************** IF ABDE - add record to the new 'autoflowAnalysisABDEStages' table *****/
10079  if ( protocol_details[ "expType" ] == "ABDE" )
10080  {
10081  // new autoflowAnalysisABDE record
10082  qry. clear();
10083  bool mwl_abde = false;
10084  for ( int ii = 0; ii < rpRange->nranges; ii++ )
10085  {
10086  if ( rpRange->chrngs[ii].wvlens.size() > 1 )
10087  {
10088  mwl_abde = true;
10089  break;
10090  }
10091  }
10092  QString etype_abde = mwl_abde ? "MWL" : "SWL";
10093  qry << "new_autoflowAnalysisABDE_record"
10094  << protocol_details[ "autoflowID" ]
10095  << etype_abde;
10096 
10097  qDebug() << "new_autoflowAnalysisABDE_record qry -- " << qry;
10098  int autoflowAnalysisABDE_ID = db->functionQuery( qry );
10099  qDebug() << "autoflowAnalysisABDE_ID: " << autoflowAnalysisABDE_ID;
10100 
10101  // new autoflowAnalysisABDEStages record
10102  qry. clear();
10103  qry << "new_autoflowAnalyisABDEstages_record" << protocol_details[ "autoflowID" ];

10649 // Function to build a Json object and document holding experiment controls
10650 QString US_ExperGuiUpload::buildJson( void )
10651 {
10652  QString js_exper("");
10653 #if QT_VERSION > 0x050000
10654 
10655  // Accumulate information on controls that have been specified
10656  int nused = sibIValue( "cells", "nused" );
10657  int nspeed = sibIValue( "speeds", "nspeeds" );
10658  int nchant = sibIValue( "solution", "nchant" );
10659  int nchanf = sibIValue( "solution", "nchanf" );
10660  int nchanu = sibIValue( "solution", "nchanu" );
10661  int nuniqs = sibIValue( "solutions", "nusols" );
10662  int solu_done = sibIValue( "solutions", "alldone" );
10663  int rngs_done = sibIValue( "ranges", "alldone" );
10664  QString v_run = sibSValue( "general", "runID" );
10665  QString v_proj = sibSValue( "general", "project" );
10666  QString v_invid = sibSValue( "general", "investigator" );
10667  QString v_dbdisk = sibSValue( "general", "dbdisk" );
10668  QString v_lab = sibSValue( "rotor", "lab" );
10669  QString v_rotor = sibSValue( "rotor", "rotor" );
10670  QString v_calib = sibSValue( "rotor", "calib" );
10671  QString v_centp = QString::number( nused );
10672  QString v_nspeed = QString::number( nspeed );
10673  QString v_nsolct = QString::number( nchant );
10674  QString v_nsolcf = QString::number( nchanf );
10675  QString v_nsolcu = QString::number( nchanu );
10676  QString v_nsolun = QString::number( nuniqs );
10677 DbgLv(1) << "EGUp:bj: n speed,chant,usols" << nspeed << nchant << nuniqs;
10678 
10679  QStringList sspeed = sibLValue( "speeds", "profiles" );
10680 DbgLv(1) << "EGUp:bj: speed profiles" << sspeed;
10681  QStringList scentp = sibLValue( "cells", "centerpieces" );
10682 DbgLv(1) << "EGUp:bj: cells centerpieces" << scentp;
10683  QStringList ssolut = sibLValue( "solutions", "channel_solutions" );
10684 DbgLv(1) << "EGUp:bj: solus solus" << ssolut;
10685 
10686  bool chk_run = ! v_run .isEmpty();
10687  bool chk_project = ! v_proj.isEmpty();
10688  bool chk_centerp = ( nused > 0 );
10689  bool chk_solution = ( solu_done > 0 );
10690  bool chk_ranges = ( rngs_done > 0 );
10691 DbgLv(1) << "EGUp:bj: ck: run proj cent solu epro"
10692  << chk_run << chk_project << chk_centerp << chk_solution << chk_ranges;
10693  bool chk_vars_set = ( chk_run && chk_project &&
10694  chk_centerp && chk_solution &&
10695  chk_ranges );
10696  bool chk_sub_enab = ( chk_vars_set && connected );
10697 
10698  if ( ! chk_sub_enab )
10699  return js_exper; // Parameterization incomplete: empty return
10700 
10701  // Start building Json of experiment controls
10702  QJsonObject jo_exper;
10703  QJsonObject jo_rotor;
10704  QJsonObject jo_speed;
10705  QJsonObject jo_cells;
10706  QJsonObject jo_solut;
10707  QJsonObject jo_photo;
10708  QJsonArray ja_speed;
10709  QJsonArray ja_centp;
10710  QJsonArray ja_solut;
10711  jo_exper.insert( "run", QJsonValue( v_run ) );
10712  jo_exper.insert( "project", QJsonValue( v_proj ) );
10713  jo_exper.insert( "dbdisk", QJsonValue( v_dbdisk ) );
10714  jo_exper.insert( "investigator", QJsonValue( v_invid ) );
10715  jo_rotor.insert( "laboratory", v_lab );
10716  jo_rotor.insert( "rotor", v_rotor );
10717  jo_rotor.insert( "calibration", v_calib );
10718  jo_exper.insert( "rotor", QJsonValue( jo_rotor ) );
10719 
10720 
10721 DbgLv(1) << "JSON_1";
10722  int jj = 0;
10723  for ( int ii = 0; ii < nspeed; ii++, jj+= 6 )
10724  {
10725  QJsonObject jo_sstep;
10726  jo_sstep.insert( "speed", QJsonValue( sspeed[ jj ] ) );
10727  jo_sstep.insert( "acceleration", QJsonValue( sspeed[ jj + 1 ] ) );
10728  QString durat = QString( "%1 h %2 m" )
10729  .arg( sspeed[ jj + 2 ] ).arg( sspeed[ jj + 3 ] );
10730  QString delay = QString( "%1 h %2 m" )
10731  .arg( sspeed[ jj + 4 ] ).arg( sspeed[ jj + 5 ] );
10732  jo_sstep.insert( "duration", QJsonValue( durat ) );
10733  jo_sstep.insert( "delay", QJsonValue( delay ) );
10734  ja_speed.append( jo_sstep );
10735  }
10736  jo_exper.insert( "speeds", ja_speed );
10737 
10738 
10739 DbgLv(1) << "JSON_2";
10740  for ( int ii = 0; ii < scentp.count(); ii++ )
10741  {
10742  QJsonObject jo_centp;
10743  QString centp = scentp[ ii ];
10744  QString scell = QString( centp ).section( ":", 0, 0 )
10745  .section( " ", 1, 1 ).simplified();
10746  QString scent = QString( centp ).section( ":", 1, 1 ).simplified();
10747  jo_centp.insert( "cell", QJsonValue( scell ) );
10748  if ( ! scent.contains( "counterbalance" ) )
10749  {
10750  int iopp = scent.lastIndexOf( "(" );
10751  QString swind = QString( scent ).mid( iopp + 2 ).section( " ", 0, 0 );
10752  scent = QString( scent ).left( iopp ).simplified();
10753  jo_centp.insert( "centerpiece", QJsonValue( scent ) );
10754  jo_centp.insert( "window_type", QJsonValue( swind ) );
10755  }
10756  else
10757  {
10758  jo_centp.insert( "counterbalance", QJsonValue( scent ) );
10759  }
10760 
10761  ja_centp.append( jo_centp );
10762  }
10763  jo_exper.insert( "centerpieces", ja_centp );
10764 
10765 
10766 DbgLv(1) << "JSON_3";
10767  for ( int ii = 0; ii < ssolut.count(); ii++ )
10768  {
10769  QJsonObject jo_solut;
10770  QString solut = ssolut[ ii ];
10771  QString scech = QString( solut ).section( ":", 0, 0 ).simplified();
10772  QString ssolu = QString( solut ).section( ":", 1, 1 ).simplified();
10773  QString scell = QString( scech ).section( "/", 0, 0 ).simplified();
10774  QString schan = QString( scech ).section( "/", 1, 1 ).simplified();
10775  jo_solut.insert( "cell", QJsonValue( scell ) );
10776  jo_solut.insert( "channel", QJsonValue( schan ) );
10777  jo_solut.insert( "solution", QJsonValue( ssolu ) );
10778 
10779  ja_solut.append( jo_solut );
10780  }
10781  jo_exper.insert( "solutions", ja_solut );
10782 
10783 DbgLv(1) << "JSON_4";
10784 
10785  // Format the byte array and string form of Json
10786  QJsonDocument jd_exper( jo_exper );
10787  QByteArray jb_exper;
10788  jb_exper = jd_exper.toJson();
10789  js_exper = QString( jb_exper );
10790 /*DEBUG*/
10791 DbgLv(1) << "EGUp:bj: js_exper" << js_exper;
10792 QString urunid=QString( v_run ).replace( " ", "_" );
10793 QString rpath=US_Settings::resultDir() + "/" + urunid + "/";
10794 QString fname=urunid + ".experiment-json.dat";
10795 QString fpath=rpath+fname;
10796 QDir rdir;
10797 if(! rdir.exists(rpath) ) rdir.mkpath(rpath);
10798 QFile jfile(fpath);
10799 if(jfile.open(QIODevice::WriteOnly|QIODevice::Text))
10800 {
10801  int flen=jb_exper.count();
10802  QDataStream* fso = new QDataStream( &jfile );
10803  fso->writeRawData( jb_exper.constData(), flen );
10804  jfile.close();
10805 }
10806 else
10807  qDebug() << "*ERROR* Unable to open file" << fpath;
10808 /*DEBUG*/
10809 
10810 #endif
10811  return js_exper;
10812 }
